      • burstMode

        public static void burstMode(int x,
                             int y)
        Parameters:
        x - x is the row number of cell which called it
        y - y is the row number of cell which called it it will call move method of CELL class on all the possible neighbors in all possible directions(according to row and column value) On whom to call move method is decided by row and column value. e.g. if cell is in corner then only call the two possible cells and so on
